---
title: Philly-Style Cheesy Beef Subs with Loaded Bacon Potatoes & Burger Sauce
description: This sub is the king of sandwiches, packed full of Philly-style flavours. Beef and onion have been cooked down and smothered in oozy cheese before being packed into a toasty brioche bun with burger sauce. Add a serving of Kiwi-spiced potatoes loaded with charred corn and nuggets of golden bacon for the ultimate side!
